{"tid":2072002,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"《塔羅》並不神秘，應該點樣問塔羅問題！","createTime":"2020-06-20T09:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T10:47:58.000Z","uid":300172,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b4d7c5cb43c669dd6eb8e048c54452c57a1c5d3","tid":2072002,"uid":300172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"玩左塔羅多年，經常幫人睇牌，經常被問到些同一様嘅問題。例如：我可以幾時出pool? 我同分手男朋友可以幾時復合？我幾時搵到一份好工？如果是這樣問，塔羅並不是不會給你真正嘅答案，但塔羅顯示出黎嘅答案未必真正幫到提問者，點解呢？大家可以思考一下，我再提出我嘅見解，同埋可以指出應該點様問塔羅⋯"},{"pid":"2691c2a0d3bdcb399ed9b4e5555ad63fc011684b","tid":2072002,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8cbe9a2b5d01238d683eb5938f309812442f7ae8","tid":2072002,"uid":6473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"5ec9a856d2fe480ccdb6475c2c2434473ac08d62","tid":2072002,"uid":300172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"其實問題的關鍵在於提問者有否對所問嘅問題負責，抑或她會將責任交付到塔羅身上"},{"pid":"b22a09d2fd1a5f824726b7bda12d532aacaee14c","tid":2072002,"uid":112482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"即係點"},{"pid":"4d7d3c2eaa4668524f34e5ccdf05be99c0b11a24","tid":2072002,"uid":300172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b22a09d2fd1a5f824726b7bda12d532aacaee14c","tid":2072002,"uid":112482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"即係點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"例如你問：我幾時會出pool?<br />\n<br />\n呢個問法可能係有d不負責任，因為你可能什麼也冇做。但其實問得呢個問題，背後一定會係希望出pool, 所以比較負責任嘅問法係我需要做d咩先可以出pool!"},{"pid":"b42357445ad559d8c1587a0586ef397d0322a70b","tid":2072002,"uid":300172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d7d3c2eaa4668524f34e5ccdf05be99c0b11a24","tid":2072002,"uid":300172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b22a09d2fd1a5f824726b7bda12d532aacaee14c","tid":2072002,"uid":1124